            <div class="rule">
                <span class="rule-number">1</span>
                <div class="rule-content">
                    <h3>Verify Trust Before Use</h3>
                    <p>AI-generated code contains <strong>1.75x more logic errors</strong> than human code (ACM 2025). Test everything, peer review AI output like you would a junior dev's PR.</p>
                    <div class="rule-metric">
                        <span class="metric-tag">1.75x more logic errors</span>
                        <span class="metric-tag">ACM 2025</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rule">
                <span class="rule-number">2</span>
                <div class="rule-content">
                    <h3>Never Approve MCPs from Unknown Sources</h3>
                    <p><strong>18 CVEs</strong> disclosed, <strong>341 malicious skills</strong> detected, <strong>400+ malicious MCP servers</strong> in the wild. Use the 5-minute audit checklist before installing any MCP server.</p>
                    <div class="rule-metric">
                        <span class="metric-tag">18 CVEs</span>
                        <span class="metric-tag">341 malicious skills</span>
                        <span class="metric-tag">400+ malicious MCPs</span>
